"How is that possible?" Alex asked, her voice tinged with unease. "The power‚Äôs supposed to be off in that section. I checked earlier. There‚Äôs no way the machine could be on."

"I‚Äôll check it out," Brett said, his tone more serious now. He grabbed his flashlight and moved toward the door.

