Chapter 21: Night Eight ‚Äì The Hollow Reveals Itself
The shadow at the fountain had vanished as quickly as it had appeared, but its presence lingered in the air, hanging heavy between Brett and Claire. The silence in the security room was now unbearable, amplified by the storm still raging outside. Claire‚Äôs hands shook as she stared at the now-empty monitors, her thoughts racing, heart pounding.

